One Move Captures Black (20)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to Play.\b0
\par This is a very high-level problem.
\par Some might give up, thinking "there is no way for white to capture black.
\par
\par In life and death problems, there are often blind spots.
\par
\par Where is the vital point to kill?
\par
\par }
