Diagram 1 (Black Stays Calm)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}{\f1\fmodern\fprq2\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \pard\nowidctlpar\qj White's cut at 1 is intended to force black to capture a stone with \b\f1 A\b0\f0 . However, black won't play like this.
\par \pard
\par Black 2 is calm. This gives black two eyes.
\par
\par If you read this sequence, black does appear to be alive. but there is in fact a move to capture black.
\par }
